</div> -->
<div class="about">
  <h2 class="about-title">About</h2>
  <p class="about-copy">
    An online platform that pairs human rights defenders, community activists, journalists and volunteers. Initially our focus is set on making a difference in Mexico but we also plan to launch globally.
  </p>
</div>
